sentences: Aslak Dørum (born 7 August 1964 in Oslo, Norway) is a Norwegian writer and bassist of the Norwegian rock band DumDum Boys.
Dørum joined DumDum Boys in 1993, after having been closely associated with them for years, and been responsible for the band's videos.
